{"tid":1254497,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"簡達華逝世","createTime":"2019-06-24T07:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:21:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f30067b18b9a6b6a7926dbb60cc45343624af2","tid":1254497,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603175350749-0603_00862_001_01b.jpg?20180603183140\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603175350749-0603_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20180603183140&h=1d1b872a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「西洋仔」簡達華腦癌病逝。<br />\n<br />\n曾經於90年代演出過電影《至尊計狀元才》、《至尊無上》、《猛鬼學堂》等共十多部電影，被稱「西洋仔」的演員簡達華，於六月一日因腦癌病逝，終年61歲。當年擅演奸角的他，曾跟譚詠麟、周潤發、曾志偉等紅星合作過。<br />\n<br />\n據知，簡達華三個月前發現患上腦癌，並令他慢慢失去記憶，離世時很安詳。本身是澳門居民的簡達華，年幼時是孤兒，與現任太太結婚超過三十年，育有一仔一女，他跟仔女感情要好，閒時更愛與兒子談車經，是一位好丈夫、好爸爸。簡達華早年在丹麥有物業，故經常澳門、丹麥兩邊走。"},{"pid":"ca977de7ec780988c6332bf8e3e4f78e30df6f31","tid":1254497,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"睇錯簡慕華"},{"pid":"8251ee8198e448138e5b9d7371bbbfeedd9deadf","tid":1254497,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"國米有無打算幫幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c82f44dcd662641d8f3caadda8baa5491a6908a","tid":1254497,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca977de7ec780988c6332bf8e3e4f78e30df6f31","tid":1254497,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"睇錯簡慕華"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"細個覺得簡慕華好靚<br />\n心諗第時大個女一定要似佢咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df939b3b66edd459f7c63e8976e4729b5b8b0207","tid":1254497,"uid":61281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:11:08.000